node.text:
@Michael_Kollosche offering this exclusive beachfront sky villa listed for $8,500,000 - Welcome home to 2702/272 Hedges Avenue, Mermaid Beach, Queensland, 4218. 

Refined beachfront living does not get any better than this brand new sky villa taking shape inside the sold out 272 Hedges Avenue tower on exclusive Hedges Avenue.

One of only two sky villas in the entire building, this exceptional residence offers 513m2 of beautifully finished interiors over levels 27 and 28 where floor-to-ceiling glass frames a Pacific Ocean outlook spanning Mermaid Beach to Coolangatta.

Entertaining is encouraged with a Gaggenau kitchen, open plan living and a wrap-around balcony fit for morning sun lounging through to sunset drinks with friends as night falls. Wake up to the sight and sound of the waves from the private master suite which enjoys its own private wing with walk-in robe and an effortlessly elegant ensuite.

For more information contact @michael_kollosche from @kollosche_

node.text:
@misslhommedieu offering this $15,750,000 Bel Air mansion (@1518belair) with over 9,300 sq ft including 6 bedrooms and 10 bathrooms - A true timeless masterpiece featuring the latest in technology, materials and infused with Old World-class and spectacular magic. Completely remodeled and completed in 2014. A state-of-the-art open floor plan, grand open kitchen/family room, and breakfast nook seating for 10. A master wing with extensive private outdoor covered patio, fireplace, infinite his and her master baths and closets designed for today's royalty. Gated circular motor-court for 10 cars with oversized 3-car garage. Extremely private with endless and breathtaking mountaintop views.

Contact @misslhommedieu or @bachiroueida for more information! @1518belair

node.text:
@EmilHartoonian offering this $4,500,000 Calabasas mansion - A magical reimagined estate, truly incomparable pedigree of quality and features behind the notable gates at The Oaks in Calabasas. This premier corner lot exudes absolute privacy and serenity. A total reimagined floor plan features French Oak hardwood flooring, a master kitchen with completely custom cabinetry and top grade built in appliances, impeccable stone counters and designer lighting accents that opens to a gracious family room perfect for large gatherings. A grand living room with open two floor ceilings, a large formal dining with custom serving built in. A custom built screening room man cave for the ultimate in home entertainment. The grand master suite is delightfully large and spacious, private seating room, an incredible custom boutique closet with island, large master spa. The secondary bedroom suites are spacious and accommodating. The spectacular grounds are the ultimate in outdoor lifestyle and entertainment. Custom trellis extends over incredible outdoor kitchen, dining area with outdoor TV and fire pit seating. Resort pool and spa, a large grass pad and custom sport court. Situated at the end of a private cul de sac with absolute privacy and the ultimate in luxury.

Contact @EmilHartoonian for more information
